~ no_code
Boss Soldier : Hey! The palace is off-limits right now. Get lost!
=> END

~ has_code
Boss Soldier : Halt. State your business.
Jarn Thorian [#sprite=attribute/neutral]: I need to enter the palace.
Boss Soldier : No entry without authorization. Go back at once.
Jarn Thorian [#sprite=attribute/neutral]: Hmm... it seems like this king really is in a "Closed Throne."
Boss Soldier : ...Who told you that?
Jarn Thorian [#sprite=attribute/neutral]: I was sent here with clearance. Check if you want.
Boss Soldier : Hmph. Fine. That's the correct phrase.
Boss Soldier : Open the way. Let this one pass.
Jarn Thorian [#sprite=attribute/neutral]: Thanks.

=> END